{"tid":1845401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗送別高比：這一消息令人心碎，高比是真正的傳奇","createTime":"2020-01-27T06:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T18:27:34.000Z","uid":173952,"like":62,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"89a647190a0bacfb76e2194e9f719104227f852a","tid":1845401,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"NBA傳奇巨星科比因直升機事故不幸離世，他的二女兒吉安娜也在飛機上。<br />\n<br />\n 在結束了尤文對那不勒斯的比賽后，C羅第一時間送上了他的哀悼，C羅寫道：&ldquo;聽到科比和他女兒吉安娜逝世這一令人心碎的消息，我真的非常難過 。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;科比是真正的傳奇，是很多人的動力來源。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;我向科比的家庭和朋友們，以及其他遇難者的家人們送去最誠摯的慰問。&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f0fe655234d1d41ae4f063816a6e73f6e656e3","tid":1845401,"uid":149494,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"足波撚：C朗忽然藍波狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb3028fe1888725eae5e1f1b757e82c1949173f","tid":1845401,"uid":173952,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"2個都訓練狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba036a92061beea0b75365d79755a5e76d2aae8b","tid":1845401,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91f0fe655234d1d41ae4f063816a6e73f6e656e3","tid":1845401,"uid":149494,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"足波撚：C朗忽然藍波狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:58:55.000Z","msg":"全世界都喊緊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3c8088498d2e38a6a7e447e2e3f43b4840a0ff","tid":1845401,"uid":15084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"acb3028fe1888725eae5e1f1b757e8